{"tid":2223869,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"渣打未經客戶批准 將銀行資金過數至馬會投注戶口 網上受害者眾","createTime":"2020-09-30T06:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T15:11:59.000Z","uid":66271,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ef2b77ba33e94a7cce70317e337a30c763d3b17a","tid":2223869,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9EARZP-Lj9y_HiUu9n0a94rVHVs=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UTIXXO6FFJGCHJ5KGIVA4MF2P4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9EARZP-Lj9y_HiUu9n0a94rVHVs%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUTIXXO6FFJGCHJ5KGIVA4MF2P4.jpg&h=cc908309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n渣打銀行系統出現嚴重錯誤。多位讀者報料，昨晚至凌晨出現多筆未經登入及核准下的離奇「自動轉賬」交易，由渣打轉賬至馬會投注戶口。據了解，多位網民有同樣遭遇，有人更表示「被轉走」金額多達數十萬元。<br />\n<br />\nKen（化名）透露，在未有登入馬會賬戶及作出任何轉數指示下，系統竟自行向渣打銀行發出直接轉賬指示，三度「自動」調走資金，合共13,500元，至香港賽馬會賬戶，直至渣打戶口無足夠結存被扣除才停止，但其馬會投注戶口卻無收到入賬資料及記錄，結存亦無相應增加，形容是「賭博多年首次遇到」。<br />\n<br />\n另一讀者曾先生（化名）表示，昨日突然發現大約20條不明交易，金額全為500元或1,000元，涉額逾萬元，「我睇住成晚，見到結存係咁跌，又無入賬馬會戶口，我驚到要轉走啲錢畀朋友，仲落街撳走啲錢，全晚都瞓唔到。用咗渣打廿年，真係好離譜，咁大間銀行都出現系統問題，至今無交待過一句說話，我已經向金管局投訴」，事隔一晚，他指出「被轉走」金額已全數存入至渣打戶口，「雖然最終無損失，我精神受損，都想向渣打索償呀」。<br />\n<br />\n渣打銀行發言人回覆指，金額已回撥至受影響客戶之銀行賬戶，對引起不便致歉。本報正向馬會查詢。"},{"pid":"e5ae8d2d5f4265fbe2bf99cab22ea933232d59bc","tid":2223869,"uid":36049,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:37:54.000Z","msg":"好人好姐都唔會用渣兜既"},{"pid":"db9ccf285e5c6763a75a869ceca08c83bf718dcb","tid":2223869,"uid":68689,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:45:03.000Z","msg":"他指出「被轉走」金額已全數存入至渣打戶口，「雖然最終無損失，我精神受損，都想向渣打索償呀」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739c5ed8f1d692bd892879d98f70fba787a58e99","tid":2223869,"uid":19213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:15:49.000Z","msg":"連登神探出動<br />\n件事點會咁簡單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b4e3145d1e9e665ceaf5110ebb0407084d8654","tid":2223869,"uid":358542,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"想問如果贏咗錢班友會唔會出黎嘈"},{"pid":"3e9da3dd909185d2a4b739201b169ed51197f277","tid":2223869,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:41:06.000Z","msg":"馬會收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb233229a13a33e4295b671056d833d7e7c7600d","tid":2223869,"uid":118083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:46:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">我想問仲有冇人係渣打未退哂全款或者未退過</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5afe1d20b51eac9822164398ec5776299588ab52","tid":2223869,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb233229a13a33e4295b671056d833d7e7c7600d","tid":2223869,"uid":118083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:46:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">我想問仲有冇人係渣打未退哂全款或者未退過</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a118fbed042b02b8a68e2f33f9e5faa1f3c8f8","tid":2223869,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48b4e3145d1e9e665ceaf5110ebb0407084d8654","tid":2223869,"uid":358542,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"想問如果贏咗錢班友會唔會出黎嘈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:21:44.000Z","msg":"On9 入錢落馬會就會贏錢？"},{"